_sText:
A fun map I made in September 2022, now ported to Gamebanana. Terrorists have made themselves known in the streets & alleyways of Gman City, causing chaos left and right, ultimately making the place desserted. The only people that remain are the terrorists & a bunch of CT's ready to stop them. Will they survive? 

Please note: There is no objective for this map, just a fun little level to kill your friends. Enjoy :))
